data.text: @silenimhuiri Hi Sheelagh, once there are more appointments available they will be added to the system, and can be booked on the following link: https://t.co/w31PNnJuXz

@HSELive @HSELive there are no booster appts available in Galway, why is this? I have tried booking multiple days in a row (at different times in day). No appts for 12+. No walkins. Checked all other county clinics and they have appts. When will Galway have availability.
@HSELive Pfizer vaccine data. Of particular interest is page 30.https://t.co/1OValJ6eua

@HSELive People may have to co-exist with Covid eventually. app Bost makes it safe and easy to communicate with users nearby. Download for free at Apple https://t.co/uChWyocMBe & Google https://t.co/Nvi0yiL0UN https://t.co/qF1gNO6kfG
